@title Provides convenient Expiring Multi Party contract utilities.
 @dev Using this library to deploy EMP's allows calling contracts to avoid importing the full EMP bytecode.

deploy(Liquidatable.ConstructorParams).details: Caller will need to register new EMP with the Registry to begin requesting prices. Caller is also responsible for enforcing constraints on `params`.
